                <div class="not-prose text-center my-6">
                    <a href={`${baseUrl}/ranges/greenpia_oh/`} class="nav-link inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-green-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-green-800 transition-colors duration-200 text-base no-underline">
                        <svg class="cta-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 21V9.975L12 3L20 9.975V21H14V14H10V21H4Z"></path></svg>
                        この練習場の施設詳細ページへ
                    </a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="sakura-gc" class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200 scroll-mt-24">
